Package: cvLM
Type: Package
Title: Cross-Validation for Linear Models
Version: 1.0
Date: 2023-12-09
Author: Philip Nye
Maintainer: Philip Nye <phipnye@gmail.com>
Description: Functions implemented in C++ leveraging Rcpp, RcppParallel, and Eigen libraries to implement cross-validation techniques for linear regression models. The code enables Leave-One-Out Cross-Validation (LOOCV) and K-Fold Cross-Validation for linear regression using Eigen matrices.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Imports: Rcpp (>= 1.0.11), RcppParallel (>= 5.1.7), RcppEigen (>= 0.3.3.7.0)
LinkingTo: Rcpp, RcppParallel, RcppEigen
SystemRequirements: GNU make
